<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.8.1">
<l>māṉkoṇṭa tōlmārvil māṇiyāy māvalimaṇ</l>
<l>tāṉkoṇṭu tāḷā laḷanta perumāṉai</l>
<l>tēṉkoṇṭa cāral tiruvēṅ kaṭattāṉai</l>
<l>nāṉceṉṟu nāṭi naṟaiyūril kaṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Going searching for the great lord who,</l>
<l>As a brahmin with a deer skin on his chest,</l>
<l>Having taken the earth from Māvali, measured [it] with his foot,</l>
<l>The one of Tiruvēṅkaṭam with hill slopes with nectar,</l>
<l rend="indent">I saw [him] in Naṟaiyūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
